						               													<description>Novi Novi TRPG is like a tabletop RPG in a box - you can sit down without preparation or a game master and start playing right away.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;First everyone picks a character card. Then the first GM picks a scene card and reads it to the scene player, and then roleplay the scene, typically ending with an ability test. Depending on how the scene is resolved the scene player gets a Light or Dark card added to their character and then the GM and scene player cards move to the next players. After three passes around the table you draw a conclusion card and figure out how your story ends.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Novi Novi is designed to be a lighthearted introduction to roleplaying for newcomers or an easy-to-use alternative for seasonsed roleplayers.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;user summary&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
